quoteDoc: TERMS OF SERVICE AND PRIVACY POLICY + COOKIE/INFORMATION POLICY
quoteText: Manybrain, Inc. collects information that your browser sends whenever you visit its website. This data may include information such as your computer's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, browser type, browser version, the pages of the Mailinator website that you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages, and other statistics.
title: The service provides details about what kinds of personal information they collect
